				<div class="contentbox-title-shading">Debian Binary Package</div>
	<div class="contentbox-noshading">
	<p>There is a Debian binary package which is available from <a href="http://apt.steve.org.uk/">my apt-get repository</a> for the Etch release of Debian GNU/Linux.  If you're using the unstable/sid branch it should be available in the official Debian repository, thanks to Radu Spineanu.</p>
<p><b>Note:</b> you will need to configure <tt>sudo</tt>, as described in the README file.</p>
